e. This may be a biased opinion, but I'd have to give it a perfect score.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-001","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Oh? Can it be...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Greetings, Michelle! So you returned to the dressing room ahead of time. A well-deserved rest, for sure.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"bye01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Michelle","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Ahh... The excitement I'm feeling has yet to die down. I get the sense that I could relive the echoing cheer of the crowd should I simply listen carefully. Do you not agree, Michelle?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Michelle","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Silently processing our achievements it would seem. 'Twas indeed a marvelous performance.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"You did especially well. It was as if you had reached new heights. Would this be a reflection of new internal developments?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Michelle","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Fufu... You need not be shy. Why not share? I'd be honored to be able to take something away from your accomplishment.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"Oh, Kaoru-san? What are you doing in-... Wait, Michelle...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Huh...? A-actually, I'm right here.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Why, hello! Kanon, Misaki!\nMichelle and I were in the middle of\nsharing our impressions of the parade.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"I-I see...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"With Michelle, huh...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"Uhm, is there someone in there...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf_left01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Nope, don't think so. Pretty sure it's empty.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"We both believe the same. It was a parade for the ages. Unfortunately, Michelle refuses to discuss the main point of interest.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Uh-huh, does she now...? And what would this 'point of interest' be?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"From her conduct on stage, I can only imagine there was a burning-hot fire in her belly, but I wish to understand what exactly changed within her heart that allowed for such unusually fierce flames.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"As a woman of the stage myself, I hope to incorporate something from her experiences into my work...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"A-ahaha...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"S-sure, okay! I get it! I actually thought her performance was much better than normal too.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"A-and I made sure to ask her myself about what happened.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"Misaki-chan...?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Is that so? And what exactly did you discover?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Well, basically...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Michelle was worried about a number of things leading up to this concert.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"She wondered what exactly she could do for Hello, Happy World!, and thought about what exactly she should be doing.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Michelle... Say it isn't so.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"But... that's when she realized. She can get on stage, give the best performance she possibly can, and make everyone smile. She figured out that that's what she can do.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"She said that she thinks she was able to do so well because she remembered her wish to make everyone smile.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"A fabulous conclusion, Michelle!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"There was one more thing...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"She said there have been times when it hurt her to worry about so many things, but she knows that every version of her is her. That if she can make someone happy by putting on an awesome show...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Then that's a version of her that she can be proud of.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Ahh... So fleeting...!\nCould it really be...?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"What happened, Kaoru-san?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"\"Every version of me is still me\". It's the same perspective I implement when attempting to embody new roles.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"To think we would take the stage with the same viewpoint... Nothing fills me with more pleasure than knowing this!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Say, I recall sharing this way of thinking with you, Misaki.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Yep. That's right.\nAnd hearing it was a really big help.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Ahh...! It seems the walls of fleetingness are closing in! Not in my wildest dreams would I have imagined having any influence on you!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"Misaki","body":"Haha... I think you're getting carried away now.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev57-ep3-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"You have both bestowed great motivation upon me. Prepare to witness an even more fleeting performance during ou